<section id="neural-os" class="mb-20">
  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold font-[family-name:var(--font-heading)] mb-6">16. Neural OS Architecture</h2>

  <div class="prose mb-8">
    <p>
      Runemate is the userspace layer of a proposed neural operating system. The architecture maps directly to the Unix/Linux model that has proven itself across five decades of systems engineering.
    </p>
  </div>

  <h3 class="text-xl font-bold font-[family-name:var(--font-heading)] mt-12 mb-4">16.1 The Linux Mapping</h3>

